svg.title: FIGURE 1 CARD - Leader knots and hitches

text.tspan: Pass and of leader through ring and double it back against
itself, making at least four turns. then pass the end
between ring and coils. Pull tight.
MATERIAL: BRISTOL BOARD, TYPE II, GRADE A .010 220M, SPECIFICATION UU-B-561,
COLOR WHITE. FIGURE 1 CARD - Leader knots and hitches
